cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.IT, cs.MM

The paper deals with image processing and specifically with demosaicking, which is a common task in computer vision and image processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a low-cost edge sensing scheme, which involves mathematical modeling and optimization, making it relevant to the categories cs.MM (Mathematical Modeling) and cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also discusses the smoothness formulation, which is related to the category cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper compares its algorithm with other demosaicking algorithms, which is relevant to the category cs.MM.
